                <head>41. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>The July 27 Operations Coordinating Board Report on <gloss target="#t_NSC1"
                        >NSC</gloss> 5811/1 stated: <list>
                        <item>“We do not recognize and do not have diplomatic relations with the
                            Albanian regime. Consequently, there has been no progress toward the
                            achievement of our objectives with respect to Albania, and there is
                            unlikely to be any until such time as the Albanian regime undertakes
                            some clear-cut initiative seeking recognition and the establishment of
                            diplomatic relations.”</item>
                    </list>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <gloss target="#t_NSC1">NSC</gloss> 5811/1 and this OCR Report are printed in
                    Part 1, <ref target="#d6">Documents 6</ref> and <ref target="#d30">30</ref>.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
